1
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:20,940
=About Love=

2
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 14=

3
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,150
Look at the time.

4
00:01:25,330 --> 00:01:26,280
It's not even daylight yet.

5
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,840
And we started makeup, right?

6
00:01:27,840 --> 00:01:28,680
After that,

7
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,790
we've been waiting here for hours.

8
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,680
Now you tell me there's no photographer?

9
00:01:31,870 --> 00:01:33,040
Are we some kind of joke to you?

10
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,560
I'm so sorry. I apologize.

11
00:01:34,710 --> 00:01:36,230
Because our photographer's mother

12
00:01:36,230 --> 00:01:37,680
had a cerebral hemorrhage this morning.

13
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,710
- Wait, how is that our problem?
- So he...

14
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,480
We're here for wedding photos.

15
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,790
Not to do charity work.

16
00:01:42,790 --> 00:01:43,840
- Yes.
- Interesting.

17
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:45,000
I'm truly sorry.

18
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,510
Please just wait a little longer.

19
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:47,950
We're already
contacting the photographer.

20
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,040
Sorry, sorry.

21
00:01:49,350 --> 00:01:51,350
Wan, call that Jinzi.

22
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:52,950
Then, Huang Hairu…

23
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,230
Ask if they're free

24
00:01:54,230 --> 00:01:55,110
to help out?

25
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:56,000
I already called, Sis.

26
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,790
It's the weekend.
All studios are swamped.

27
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,150
They can't spare anyone.

28
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:00,590
Then try to find

29
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,480
Mingming.

30
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,560
The guests upstairs are rushing.

31
00:02:02,950 --> 00:02:03,790
Take some fruit up.

32
00:02:03,950 --> 00:02:05,000
Ask them to wait a bit.

33
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:05,840
Okay.

34
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:07,200
Well, Miss Ming.

35
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,630
- Yes.
- We're only taking wedding photos

36
00:02:08,630 --> 00:02:10,630
once in our lives.

37
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,120
You gonna just grab some amateur

38
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,080
to fool us?

39
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,960
- That's too much.
- No.

40
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,870
Do you think we're

41
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:16,870
easy to push around?

42
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,080
No. You misunderstand.

43
00:02:18,150 --> 00:02:19,030
Whoever I find

44
00:02:19,030 --> 00:02:20,150
will be a professional

45
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,310
and skilled photographer.

46
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:23,800
Professional?
Making us wait hours is "professional"?

47
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,840
Stood for two hours.
My legs are swollen.

48
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,150
I'm really sorry about that.

49
00:02:27,150 --> 00:02:29,240
How about having some water and snacks.

50
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,000
- Take a break.
- What's wrong with you two?

51
00:02:31,410 --> 00:02:32,750
Great day for wedding photos.

52
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:33,960
Why so angry?

53
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:36,430
Who are you? None of your business!

54
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:37,960
I'm a photographer.

55
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,240
You're just a fill-in, huh?

56
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,310
Sorry.

57
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:43,680
We're not doing
the wedding photos.

58
00:02:43,910 --> 00:02:45,030
We want financial compensation.

59
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,360
Lost wages and emotional damages.

60
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,590
Calculate it quickly. Hurry.

61
00:02:47,590 --> 00:02:49,310
Listen, refund us and compensate.

62
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:50,550
Yeah, yeah.

63
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:51,710
Compensation is a must.

64
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:53,080
But you two came today,

65
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,800
so I'm sure it's not for compensation.

66
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,520
You came for photos, didn't you?

67
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:58,800
Here's my card.

68
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,430
I'm the photography director
at Junziyang.

69
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,190
I don't care about your "Yang" whatever.

70
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,120
Refund. Compensation.

71
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:05,960
Junziyang?

72
00:03:12,590 --> 00:03:13,780
(Junziyang Photo Studio,
Photography Director)

73
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:16,240
Isn't that studio we looked at earlier?

74
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,280
The super pricey one.

75
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,680
You...

76
00:03:20,430 --> 00:03:22,190
Photography Director at Junziyang

77
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:25,240
is now temping here?

78
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,470
Exactly.

79
00:03:28,650 --> 00:03:29,590
She's my ex-girlfriend.

80
00:03:35,630 --> 00:03:37,870
You two talked quite a bit last night.

81
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,310
I didn't expect we'd hit it off so well.

82
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,470
He's such a hopeless romantic.

83
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:45,280
You know how much he likes you, right?

84
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,120
I know.

85
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,280
Goes to show I'm a decent person.

86
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,120
Better that than being hated.

87
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,750
So

88
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,800
a woman with a boyfriend

89
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,960
secretly meets someone who likes her,

90
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,840
is this normal?

91
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,520
Can't I meet him for something?

92
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,430
What thing?

93
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:03,680
None of your business.

94
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,630
I saw you two chatting
so happily that day,

95
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,190
I thought you were a couple.

96
00:04:09,470 --> 00:04:10,870
He's a fun guy.

97
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,470
You'd have a good time with him too.

98
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,560
Is that a problem?

99
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:22,160
Meeting your boyfriend's
best friend in private,

100
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:23,720
besides feeling happy,

101
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,430
it's mostly thrilling, isn't it?

102
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,040
You could try it yourself.

103
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:30,190
But first, you need to have a boyfriend.

104
00:04:32,190 --> 00:04:34,160
I have standards for friends.

105
00:04:35,090 --> 00:04:35,970
Not just anyone

106
00:04:35,970 --> 00:04:37,190
can be my friend.

107
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,750
So he meets your standards?

108
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,080
More than that.

109
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,240
In my heart.

110
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,560
He holds a place as my friend.

111
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,480
Because he's kind and straightforward.

112
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:56,190
Most importantly,
he knows how to act appropriately.

113
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:59,040
You really think highly of him.

114
00:04:59,870 --> 00:05:01,430
I admire your honesty.

115
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,600
How about this.

116
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,430
Why not be honest

117
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,400
with Bei too?

118
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,870
What do I need to be honest about?

119
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:09,120
Guess our values are different.

120
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,310
Anyway, married celebrities

121
00:05:12,310 --> 00:05:14,040
I've caught meeting others secretly

122
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,680
never had your confidence.

123
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:17,630
So in your book,

124
00:05:17,630 --> 00:05:20,000
any contact with
the opposite sex is cheating?

125
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,090
Or can your camera

126
00:05:22,090 --> 00:05:23,600
read people's minds?

127
00:05:24,390 --> 00:05:25,950
Sis, you're changing the subject.

128
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:27,600
We're talking about being honest.

129
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,390
I have a habit.

130
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,160
Unimportant stuff like this.

131
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,040
I usually mention it to Bei

132
00:05:33,310 --> 00:05:34,630
when we're free.

133
00:05:34,630 --> 00:05:35,510
Casually, when it comes up,

134
00:05:35,510 --> 00:05:36,800
I'll naturally bring it up.

135
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:38,670
For example,

136
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,920
when we're lying in bed.

137
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,310
You're really smooth with words.

138
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,600
You'll probably never find

139
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,870
the right time, huh?

140
00:05:52,270 --> 00:05:53,310
Are you in a hurry?

141
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,000
How about I make an exception for you?

142
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,240
Tonight, okay?

143
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,870
I'll tell Bei

144
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,680
everything about Gong and me.

145
00:06:02,870 --> 00:06:04,680
I'll even make him remember it.

146
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:05,920
Because I know

147
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,600
An Miu prepares an exam.

148
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,120
Then I'll invite Bei

149
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,560
to my place for his exam.

150
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,070
You know, right?

151
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,190
Last week I even asked him

152
00:06:15,190 --> 00:06:16,310
to come over for drinks.

153
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,390
So tonight,
I'm going to have a word with

154
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,430
Bei about that.

155
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,560
Why didn't he take you that day

156
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,390
to our dog-friendly dinner party?

157
00:06:29,390 --> 00:06:31,190
Okay, let's start with
full-body shots first.

158
00:06:31,190 --> 00:06:32,480
Groom, you can

159
00:06:32,750 --> 00:06:34,270
arm around her, or heads together.

160
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,120
Or stand on a higher spot.

161
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,430
Hug her, yes, make it sweet.

162
00:06:36,430 --> 00:06:37,360
That's it. Okay.

163
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:38,590
Alright, come on.

164
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,600
Okay, yeah, good.

165
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,160
Smile, yeah.

166
00:06:42,390 --> 00:06:43,360
Perfect.

167
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:45,040
Now look at each other. Eye contact.

168
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,830
Yeah, good. Really good.

169
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:06,070
Back when you learned photography
from me,

170
00:07:06,530 --> 00:07:07,800
I thought you were just playing around.

171
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,040
Never thought it's your career now.

172
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,600
I like photography not because of you.

173
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:14,720
Don't overthink it.

174
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,190
He helped me open the studio.

175
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,080
Do you love him?

176
00:07:20,390 --> 00:07:22,190
Of course. Why be together if I don't?

177
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,200
Do you still love me?

178
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,240
Don't ask such pointless questions.

179
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:31,670
I have someone now.

180
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:35,800
You can't lie to yourself.

181
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:41,750
Right.

182
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,830
Then let's get this straight today.

183
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,510
I've thought about it seriously.

184
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,430
My youth

185
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,430
was destined to have someone
I pined for,

186
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,630
and that someone
just happened to be you.

187
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:59,160
I'm grateful to have you along the way,

188
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,190
but unfortunately,

189
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,830
it's also because of you.

190
00:08:05,830 --> 00:08:06,720
We've been on and off

191
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,870
so many times.

192
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,920
I've lost count.

193
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,360
I used to think

194
00:08:11,720 --> 00:08:13,190
we were special to each other,

195
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:14,800
but not special enough

196
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,240
to stop you from seeing other women.

197
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:23,160
Hey!

198
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,000
Let's shoot here.

199
00:08:24,750 --> 00:08:25,680
This place feels nice.

200
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,270
Okay.

201
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,630
Yeah.

202
00:08:32,630 --> 00:08:33,470
Take these flowers.

203
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:34,710
Tidy things up.

204
00:08:36,670 --> 00:08:37,750
We had a big misunderstanding.

205
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,360
Got curious

206
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:41,750
and found a lot of photos
on your computer.

207
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:43,390
Those models

208
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:44,870
look great on camera.

209
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,840
But I wouldn't suggest
taking pictures with them.

210
00:08:47,670 --> 00:08:49,360
Ruins the artistic vibe.

211
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:56,000
I've been meaning to ask you about this.

212
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:59,150
How did you show up so fast
to help out today?

213
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:01,320
Your receptionist Wan told me.

214
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:04,360
Slept with her too, huh?

215
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:06,240
Is that what you think of me?

216
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,790
It's fine. I'm over it.

217
00:09:10,790 --> 00:09:12,200
But I just want to advice you

218
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,670
to love someone wholeheartedly.

219
00:09:16,630 --> 00:09:17,790
You know who I mean.

220
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,910
Let's take a break.

221
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:23,750
I'll switch lenses.

222
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,120
Are we still friends?

223
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:36,480
I think in this world,

224
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,630
there are too many relationships

225
00:09:37,870 --> 00:09:39,440
that can't be summed up in one word.

226
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,630
Let's just be

227
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,390
Mingming and Lun.

228
00:09:46,530 --> 00:09:48,080
Besides, friends
aren't what you want, right?

229
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,360
We're family.

230
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:56,600
Whenever you need me,

231
00:09:57,270 --> 00:09:58,200
I'll always help you.

232
00:10:01,630 --> 00:10:02,470
Thanks.

233
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,390
But I don't like

234
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:06,030
owing favors or repaying them.

235
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,960
We're already even.

236
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,910
Let's end it here.

237
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:26,870
Come on.

238
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,510
Bro.

239
00:10:28,870 --> 00:10:29,790
It's so hot.

240
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:30,800
How about we take a break?

241
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,150
Sure, no problem.

242
00:10:32,790 --> 00:10:34,240
Let's sit here for a bit.

243
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,160
Dad.

244
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:38,030
Come on.

245
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,920
Have some water.

246
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,560
Here.

247
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,790
Tell Tian that later here

248
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,630
will be renovated in a style like this.

249
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:51,270
- Have some water.
- Thanks.

250
00:10:51,270 --> 00:10:52,120
- Sorry.
- Well done.

251
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:52,960
- Well done.
- Thanks.

252
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,080
Here you go, Sir.

253
00:10:54,080 --> 00:10:54,920
Thanks.

254
00:10:57,200 --> 00:10:58,150
Well.

255
00:10:58,150 --> 00:10:59,000
Sir,

256
00:10:59,000 --> 00:10:59,870
can I ask you something?

257
00:11:00,270 --> 00:11:01,240
Later, could you

258
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,790
take a group photo of the three of us?

259
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,200
Just something simple.

260
00:11:06,790 --> 00:11:07,630
No problem.

261
00:11:08,390 --> 00:11:09,230
Thanks.

262
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:12,200
When we were taking pictures,

263
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,600
my wife was gossiping.

264
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,840
She was wondering
how you two ended things.

265
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,200
So I told my wife,

266
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,870
with the way you two get along now,

267
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,240
at least,

268
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,080
no, definitely,

269
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,670
it's not because of cheating, right?

270
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:27,920
Actually...

271
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,200
Actually, we…

272
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,320
It was me.

273
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:33,550
I found someone new.

274
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:39,720
Take this to them to drink.

275
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:41,910
Sorry about that.

276
00:11:43,390 --> 00:11:45,630
Forget it, Sir.
No need to talk about sad stuff.

277
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:47,040
Well,

278
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,550
but let me tell you, buddy,

279
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,270
you gotta cheer up.

280
00:11:52,510 --> 00:11:53,350
Let's take the shot now.

281
00:11:53,810 --> 00:11:55,150
If we wait longer,
we'll lose the light.

282
00:11:55,630 --> 00:11:56,750
Alright, let's shoot.

283
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:58,670
Hey, wait, wait a sec.

284
00:11:58,910 --> 00:11:59,870
You stand in the middle.

285
00:12:00,030 --> 00:12:01,000
You stand in the middle.

286
00:12:01,630 --> 00:12:02,740
- Come on.
- Okay.

287
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,670
Yes, perfect.

288
00:12:08,820 --> 00:12:11,660
(Zhen Guan)

289
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:26,230
Xi.

290
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:28,560
Yeah?

291
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,910
What do you think of

292
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,150
An Miu?

293
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,160
She's cute.

294
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,280
Anything else?

295
00:12:38,870 --> 00:12:40,790
Stop asking, you won't like the answer.

296
00:12:41,270 --> 00:12:42,480
She just got back from abroad.

297
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,960
She hardly any friends, so I thought

298
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,960
I'd introduce you two.

299
00:12:48,270 --> 00:12:49,110
Oh.

300
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,790
Guess she won't be on my friend list.

301
00:12:52,510 --> 00:12:53,480
She's

302
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,550
just a bit straightforward,

303
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:57,150
not very emotionally intelligent.

304
00:12:57,670 --> 00:12:58,630
But she's

305
00:12:58,870 --> 00:12:59,840
a good person.

306
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:05,270
Did she ever talk about

307
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,150
his time in the UK?

308
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,720
There's one thing

309
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,360
I've always been curious about.

310
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:20,120
Why did you go abroad to
study luxury goods appraisal?

311
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:23,440
It doesn't seem like your hobby.

312
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,670
Back in college,

313
00:13:31,030 --> 00:13:32,080
a friend told me

314
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:34,120
vintage bags had a strong market.

315
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:37,000
At first, I actually
made some good money.

316
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:39,200
But later
I bought a batch of counterfeits,

317
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:41,270
and ended up losing everything.

318
00:13:41,870 --> 00:13:42,910
So I made up my mind

319
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:44,150
to study abroad for a while.

320
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:49,800
That period

321
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,550
must've been really tough, right?

322
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,510
It was,

323
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:58,150
but I got through it.

324
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:01,150
We've known each other for five years.

325
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:03,030
No, six years.

326
00:14:03,630 --> 00:14:04,790
Too long.

327
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,550
I know everything about him.

328
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:09,150
I've had plenty of time alone with Bei.

329
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:10,790
We often

330
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,440
shopped together and cooked together.

331
00:14:12,870 --> 00:14:14,270
During exam season,

332
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,720
he'd come to my room at night

333
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,790
to tutor me.

334
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,360
I have a question.

335
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,040
Hmm?

336
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,320
Answer me honestly.

337
00:14:24,150 --> 00:14:24,990
Go ahead.

338
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:28,030
If An Miu and I both fell into
the water, who would you save?

339
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,390
Only choose between me and An Miu.

340
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,550
No other answers.

341
00:14:36,030 --> 00:14:37,200
Definitely you.

342
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:40,440
Really?

343
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:41,630
I mean it.

344
00:14:41,840 --> 00:14:43,200
She's like a little sister to me.

345
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,870
What if you had to cut off

346
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:47,510
contact with one of us,

347
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:48,600
who would you choose?

348
00:14:51,870 --> 00:14:54,360
I'd definitely choose to be with you.

349
00:14:55,390 --> 00:14:57,080
Did An Miu say something to you?

350
00:14:57,750 --> 00:14:58,600
Don't...

351
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,200
Come in.

352
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,080
Am I

353
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:11,030
interrupting?

354
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,280
No.

355
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,960
What's up, Yu He?

356
00:15:15,290 --> 00:15:16,150
I...

357
00:15:16,150 --> 00:15:16,990
You're here.

358
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:18,630
Let's go.

359
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:23,720
You two had plans?

360
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:26,480
Yeah, Yu He wants to

361
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,000
check out a coffee shop.

362
00:15:29,910 --> 00:15:31,600
Ah, yeah.

363
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,080
Alright, you guys go ahead.

364
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:35,320
Okay, we're leaving.

365
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,440
Bye bye.

366
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:41,740
(Zhen Guan)

367
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:45,560
Sorry.

368
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,600
Come sit in my shop for a bit.

369
00:15:49,750 --> 00:15:50,590
Sure.

370
00:15:57,390 --> 00:15:58,230
What's wrong?

371
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,750
I feel like
I've seen that person before.

372
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,200
Can't remember where.

373
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,750
Maybe I'm just mistaken.

374
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:07,920
Let's go.

375
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,270
When I first met Gong,

376
00:16:11,270 --> 00:16:12,550
Bei was single.

377
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,790
I thought about
setting him up with one of my friends.

378
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,000
But it never worked out.

379
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,630
So I've always wondered

380
00:16:17,630 --> 00:16:19,870
what kind of girl Bei likes.

381
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:21,960
Never thought it'd be you.

382
00:16:22,870 --> 00:16:24,000
Are you still helping…

383
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:25,120
Not anymore.

384
00:16:28,240 --> 00:16:29,480
I was just passing by today.

385
00:16:29,750 --> 00:16:31,360
I wanted to tell Bei

386
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,240
I'm getting married.

387
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:34,960
Congrats.

388
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,320
So that's why you came.

389
00:16:38,910 --> 00:16:39,750
Mm.

390
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:42,790
My bad for overthinking.

391
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:46,320
You want him to tell Gong?

392
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:54,120
You and Gong...

393
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,240
I know he never got over you.

394
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,240
He never got over Jiang Yifan.

395
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:05,030
Has nothing to do with me.

396
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,550
And now it has nothing to do
with you either.

397
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:12,070
So lately, I've been thinking a lot.

398
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:14,830
If I hadn't come to you back then,

399
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,960
what would things be like with Gong now?

400
00:17:18,510 --> 00:17:19,960
No one can say for sure about

401
00:17:21,030 --> 00:17:22,030
things that never happened.

402
00:17:26,510 --> 00:17:27,960
Bei's a really good guy.

403
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:29,510
You gotta treat him right.

404
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,150
I know.

405
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:34,000
I'm not like his ex-girlfriend.

406
00:17:35,750 --> 00:17:37,110
No matter what happens,

407
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:38,720
I won't give up on Bei that easily.

408
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:41,640
You know about Zhen?

409
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:44,510
Bei told you?

410
00:17:45,550 --> 00:17:46,390
Yeah.

411
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,720
Zhen Guan actually uses Zhen's name.

412
00:17:53,030 --> 00:17:54,720
Bei used to never bring that up before.

413
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,920
So I was honestly surprised.

414
00:17:57,750 --> 00:17:59,030
Guess he's really moved on.

415
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,480
People have to move forward.

416
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:05,590
You're doing the same, aren't you?

417
00:18:06,830 --> 00:18:07,670
Yeah.

418
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,270
If I get married,

419
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,270
I probably wouldn't invite them.

420
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,830
So whether he knows or not

421
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,510
doesn't really matter.

422
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,440
About Bei,

423
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:21,680
I didn't plan to talk about it before,

424
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:23,880
and I won't bring it up later either.

425
00:18:26,640 --> 00:18:27,480
Thanks.

426
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:48,590
Why do I feel like Yu He just now

427
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:51,030
still can't get over Gong?

428
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:58,110
You don't actually believe An Miu,
do you?

429
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,680
Stuff like that
doesn't happen these days.

430
00:19:02,160 --> 00:19:03,830
But if there was nothing going on,

431
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:05,550
why would he mention Zhen Guan

432
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,310
but not Zhen?

433
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:08,640
Bringing up an ex?

434
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,400
Who in their right mind brings up an ex?

435
00:19:11,310 --> 00:19:13,160
What did Gong say when you asked him?

436
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,110
He didn't say much.

437
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,270
Maybe it wasn't something
he could talk about.

438
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,480
Xiaoxi,

439
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,480
if you really care,

440
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:23,110
why not just ask Bei directly?

441
00:19:23,790 --> 00:19:24,830
Can't say it.

442
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:28,680
I don't even know why.

443
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:30,750
It's such a simple question.

444
00:19:33,780 --> 00:19:35,140
(Zeyan)

445
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:36,960
Maybe because I have so many things

446
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,240
I haven't told him clearly.

447
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,240
Guess I don't have the right to ask.

448
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,550
Or maybe,

449
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:47,480
I'm scared of the answer.

450
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:53,340
(Zeyan)

451
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:56,440
What's wrong?
Your phone's been ringing nonstop.

452
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,200
Did you two fight?

453
00:20:00,270 --> 00:20:01,110
No.

454
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:02,480
I don't want to see him.

455
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:06,640
What happened?

456
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,280
His

457
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,750
ex-girlfriend

458
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:16,640
found my account

459
00:20:17,110 --> 00:20:18,550
somehow,

460
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,070
and sent me messages.

461
00:20:20,830 --> 00:20:22,070
Sent you messages?

462
00:20:22,070 --> 00:20:22,910
Yeah.

463
00:20:23,070 --> 00:20:24,720
Going on and on
about their past relationship.

464
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,070
With pictures and captions.

465
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:27,590
Is she crazy?

466
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:28,550
Totally off.

467
00:20:28,550 --> 00:20:29,400
Why'd she send that?

468
00:20:29,590 --> 00:20:30,790
Just trying to get under my skin.

469
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:32,830
Does your boyfriend know?

470
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:34,920
No, I haven't told him.

471
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,400
Do you think I should tell him?

472
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,550
I can't say anything.

473
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:40,350
Every time something happens,

474
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:41,550
I run to question him.

475
00:20:42,830 --> 00:20:43,830
That's so childish.

476
00:20:44,960 --> 00:20:46,440
Makes me look so immature.

477
00:20:46,750 --> 00:20:47,960
No, can't ask.

478
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:51,000
You're mature.

479
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,750
You've got all the big words ready.

480
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:54,310
If you were really mature,

481
00:20:54,310 --> 00:20:55,830
why are you throwing a fit here?

482
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:58,160
I'm not throwing a fit. I just…

483
00:20:58,160 --> 00:21:00,240
I can't face him. How am I supposed to?

484
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:02,350
The moment I see him,
my mind's flooded with those words

485
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,550
and those photos.

486
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:05,510
Wait, how is this any different from me?

487
00:21:07,310 --> 00:21:08,960
I've realized that in love,

488
00:21:09,590 --> 00:21:11,270
no one can truly stay cool.

489
00:21:12,790 --> 00:21:13,750
Exactly.

490
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:21,590
Wait, why

491
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,590
aren't you answering my calls?

492
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:26,440
I don't wanna answer, so I don't.

493
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:32,830
If you're upset about something,
or want me to change,

494
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,200
just tell me.

495
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,480
Nothing to say.

496
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:46,830
Can I hitch a ride with you two later?

497
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:47,920
Drop me off?

498
00:21:48,270 --> 00:21:49,270
I didn't drive today.

499
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,800
Ask him.

500
00:21:54,480 --> 00:21:55,550
Wherever you are, I'm there.

501
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,790
Get in my car,

502
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:58,030
and I'll drop her off.

503
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:03,590
Let's go.

504
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:04,670
Let's go.

505
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,750
Don't touch me.

506
00:22:18,270 --> 00:22:19,590
Why can't I touch you?

507
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:22,310
You're the one
who didn't answer my calls.

508
00:22:23,750 --> 00:22:25,070
Just call me Yingtao.

509
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:27,110
"Yingtao" in "Yingtaoxiaozui".
[*Yingtaoxiaozui: Small mouth like cherry]

510
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:32,790
I'll answer if I want,
and I won't if I don't.

511
00:22:32,790 --> 00:22:33,720
So what?

512
00:22:36,580 --> 00:22:40,100
(Li Xiaoxi)

513
00:22:40,790 --> 00:22:41,640
Bei.

514
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,030
Did I leave my bag in your office?

515
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:44,590
It's at my shop.

516
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,880
I'll bring it back to you tonight.

517
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:47,640
Oh.

518
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:48,680
What do you want to eat tonight?

519
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:50,110
I'll be back later.

520
00:22:50,310 --> 00:22:51,440
You eat first, don't wait for me.

521
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:53,270
Mm. See you tonight.

522
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:55,040
Bye bye.

523
00:22:56,790 --> 00:22:57,630
What's wrong?

524
00:22:57,700 --> 00:22:58,960
Is there something important
in your bag?

525
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:01,350
Nothing important.

526
00:23:01,790 --> 00:23:02,830
- Let's go.
- Where's the car?

527
00:23:16,260 --> 00:23:18,740
(An Miu)

528
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,640
Have you met any of her other friends?

529
00:23:27,160 --> 00:23:28,030
Is it not the right time,

530
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,310
or does she not want you to meet them?

531
00:23:29,720 --> 00:23:31,720
Looks like
you don't know her that well either.

532
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:56,940
(Missed call from An Miu)

533
00:24:18,030 --> 00:24:18,870
You sure

534
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:20,510
you don't wanna grab a meal together?

535
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:22,520
No.

536
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,510
We have plans tonight.

537
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:26,910
And also…

538
00:24:28,440 --> 00:24:29,640
Don't come to me again.

539
00:24:30,550 --> 00:24:31,480
Take it as doing me a favor.

540
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:37,480
Okay.

541
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:39,840
Relax.

542
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:47,920
Can I just look at you a little longer?

543
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,030
Nothing left to see.

544
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,160
Don't you have plenty of photos?

545
00:24:55,240 --> 00:24:56,080
Watch however you want.

546
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,520
I'm leaving.

547
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:00,240
Stay safe.

548
00:25:38,030 --> 00:25:39,920
Are you never gonna talk to me again?

549
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:50,750
I don't know what to say.

550
00:25:51,310 --> 00:25:52,960
I explained everything clearly.

551
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,480
Do you want me to say it again?

552
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,270
This morning at our store,

553
00:25:57,270 --> 00:25:59,240
the client's photographer really...

554
00:25:59,240 --> 00:26:00,350
I heard it loud and clear.

555
00:26:01,070 --> 00:26:02,590
Your store ran into trouble.

556
00:26:03,350 --> 00:26:05,270
And somehow he just knew.

557
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,790
So he rushed over to play the hero.

558
00:26:07,240 --> 00:26:08,680
I didn't ask him to come.

559
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:10,640
I asked Wan to call

560
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,830
several photographers we know,

561
00:26:11,830 --> 00:26:13,240
but they were all busy.

562
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:14,790
Only he had free time.

563
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:17,550
On call 24/7,
ready to serve you anytime.

564
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:20,350
Why not just hire him
as your personal assistant?

565
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:25,280
First of all,

566
00:26:25,790 --> 00:26:28,270
Wan called him on her own.

567
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:31,240
Second, he's swamped.

568
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:32,550
He's booked solid till next year.

569
00:26:33,510 --> 00:26:34,350
Impressive.

570
00:26:34,720 --> 00:26:36,110
He's so amazing.

571
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,160
I really should thank him.

572
00:26:38,310 --> 00:26:40,550
I thank him, thank him, thank you.

573
00:26:40,550 --> 00:26:42,350
Stop with that sarcastic tone.

574
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:43,720
When I was in trouble,

575
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:45,550
I just wanted someone to help me.

576
00:26:45,830 --> 00:26:47,030
Did you ever care about me?

577
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:48,070
But did you call me?

578
00:26:48,270 --> 00:26:49,790
Did you ever try calling me?

579
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:51,400
Who's your boyfriend anyway?

580
00:26:51,400 --> 00:26:52,830
What good would calling you do?

581
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:55,030
Who else do you know
in the photography circle besides me?

582
00:26:55,640 --> 00:26:57,000
You'd just panic with me.

583
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,720
And I'd still have to fix it myself.

584
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,160
I just don't get it.

585
00:27:00,350 --> 00:27:02,550
So what if we lose this order
and pay a little compensation?

586
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:04,350
Are you that short on cash?

587
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,440
Are you just using this chance

588
00:27:05,440 --> 00:27:06,550
to meet him again?

589
00:27:06,550 --> 00:27:08,350
Do I need to wait till now
to meet him again?

590
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:14,030
Can't help, and you won't let others.

591
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:15,270
Are you a man?

592
00:27:19,830 --> 00:27:20,670
Yeah.

593
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,720
I'm not a man.

594
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,000
He is!

595
00:27:24,640 --> 00:27:25,510
Is there a day

596
00:27:25,510 --> 00:27:26,440
when I'm useless

597
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:27,640
that you'll go back to him?

598
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,270
How can you be so dirty-minded?

599
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:30,200
Me? Dirty-minded?

600
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,160
My girlfriend

601
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:33,200
spent the whole day with her ex.

602
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,080
If I hadn't seen it myself,

603
00:27:34,090 --> 00:27:35,270
I'd still be like an idiot!

604
00:27:35,270 --> 00:27:36,480
Let me say this one last time.

605
00:27:37,550 --> 00:27:39,000
He came here to help.

606
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,830
If you were in trouble

607
00:27:40,830 --> 00:27:42,550
and your ex came to help,
would you turn her down?

608
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,390
I would!

609
00:27:43,540 --> 00:27:44,830
Because I know how to avoid suspicion.

610
00:27:44,830 --> 00:27:46,000
Am I a suspect?

611
00:27:46,220 --> 00:27:47,070
If I were dying,

612
00:27:47,070 --> 00:27:48,270
and waiting for your ex to save me,

613
00:27:48,270 --> 00:27:49,680
would you still turn her away for me?

614
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:51,790
I never doubted you,
so why do you need to avoid anything?

615
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:54,110
Don't throw out
those ridiculous examples.

616
00:27:54,550 --> 00:27:56,000
Here's a realistic one.

617
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:58,030
If he hadn't helped me today,

618
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:00,750
I'd have to pay
tens of thousands in penalties.

619
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:02,160
If they had connections

620
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,240
and wanted to shut me down,

621
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:05,440
it wouldn't be tens of thousands
or hundreds of thousands.

622
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:06,720
Tell me, what should I do then?

623
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,960
Would avoiding suspicion fix anything?

624
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:09,350
Fine, so according to you,

625
00:28:09,350 --> 00:28:10,510
he's your big investor now.

626
00:28:10,510 --> 00:28:12,310
You two can openly keep in touch then.

627
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:14,440
Otherwise, you'd be losing millions!

628
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,110
So scary. Millions!

629
00:28:17,110 --> 00:28:18,480
Do you really need to be like this?

630
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:20,920
Just because he's my ex?

631
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:22,910
Right now, I feel...

632
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,560
Like I somehow broke you two apart.

633
00:28:24,770 --> 00:28:25,980
Should I just call him now?

634
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:26,830
Ask him to come over.

635
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:27,790
Why stay in the car?

636
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:29,160
Just come right here, right here!

637
00:28:29,160 --> 00:28:30,960
Why do you always assume meeting an ex

638
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,640
has to be something like that?

639
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,830
I don't think about anything else,

640
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,790
so I can face him so calmly now.

641
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:45,070
I don't love him anymore,
but I don't hate him either.

642
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:47,000
I'm your girlfriend now.

643
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,960
Why can't you trust me?

644
00:28:51,720 --> 00:28:53,030
I don't believe

645
00:28:55,290 --> 00:28:57,310
that our relationship of a few days

646
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:59,680
can surpass your relationship
of several years.

647
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,550
I also can't convince myself

648
00:29:01,550 --> 00:29:03,000
that my girlfriend spending a whole day

649
00:29:03,000 --> 00:29:03,840
with her ex-boyfriend and

650
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,270
staying in the car with him
for so long

651
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,480
is totally right!

652
00:29:07,480 --> 00:29:09,350
Then you should have found a girl

653
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,790
who has never
fallen in love with others.

654
00:29:12,790 --> 00:29:14,550
Don't I even have the right
to be jealous?

655
00:29:15,270 --> 00:29:16,790
Am I not allowed to have any feelings?

656
00:29:16,790 --> 00:29:18,830
If you saw me with my ex-girlfriend,

657
00:29:18,830 --> 00:29:20,640
would you be angry?
Would you go crazy?

658
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,040
Yeah.

659
00:29:23,310 --> 00:29:24,150
You wouldn't.

660
00:29:25,480 --> 00:29:28,240
Because… because I don't have
an ex-girlfriend at all.

661
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:30,480
I'm such a fool.

662
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:31,400
I deserve it!

663
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:33,240
I waited for a woman for seven years!

664
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,590
Then go find another woman!

665
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:37,880
Would that be fair?

666
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:40,200
Would you not feel so wronged then?

667
00:29:41,070 --> 00:29:43,000
If that girl is better than me, tell me.

668
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:45,550
I'll let you go.

669
00:29:56,310 --> 00:29:58,240
Did you ever love me at all?

670
00:30:01,020 --> 00:30:01,880
Now I'm not sure

671
00:30:01,880 --> 00:30:03,480
if I'm the one you want.

672
00:30:30,830 --> 00:30:32,680
This isn't the life I want.

673
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,510
If today's argument

674
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:37,960
is just the beginning,

675
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,070
I really don't know

676
00:30:41,070 --> 00:30:42,510
how we'll get through the days ahead.

677
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:07,110
Can you promise me

678
00:31:08,790 --> 00:31:11,070
you won't see him again, okay?

679
00:31:12,590 --> 00:31:14,400
I can only promise not to see him.

680
00:31:17,270 --> 00:31:18,110
What do you mean?

681
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:19,520
Exactly what I said.

682
00:31:22,790 --> 00:31:24,200
So you mean
he can still come to see you.

683
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:28,110
I already told him not to come again.

684
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:29,960
But if he insists on coming,

685
00:31:29,960 --> 00:31:31,310
I can't stop him.

686
00:31:32,270 --> 00:31:33,160
Unless I shut down my shop,

687
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,310
and stay home all day.

688
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:44,880
If I go fight him right now,

689
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,400
- would you agree?
- Are you crazy?

690
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:47,400
Yeah, I am crazy!

691
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,960
Why do you have such childish ideas?

692
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:50,310
Do you want me to humiliate myself?

693
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,110
Do whatever you want, okay?

694
00:31:57,110 --> 00:31:58,400
Do whatever you want.

695
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:16,080
Wait, what's wrong?

696
00:32:16,350 --> 00:32:17,750
Where are you going with that luggage?

697
00:32:20,030 --> 00:32:20,870
I want to go home.

698
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,790
Wait, did I do something wrong

699
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,030
to upset you?

700
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,400
It's not you.

701
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,350
It's me.

702
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:33,720
I've been hiding a lot from you.

703
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:36,270
I'm scared if I tell you,

704
00:32:36,270 --> 00:32:37,550
you'll leave me.

705
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,440
Wait, what is it?

706
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,310
It's about my past.

707
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,070
I once caused
several couples to break up.

708
00:32:53,350 --> 00:32:55,070
That includes Gong and Yu He.

709
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,080
Actually,

710
00:33:04,720 --> 00:33:05,960
I'm Jiang Yifan.

711
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,160
You seem distracted today.

712
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:53,000
Do you think I deserve to be loved?

713
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,880
I used to think
there were no good men in the world,

714
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,880
but never stopped to wonder

715
00:33:59,880 --> 00:34:01,310
if I'm a bad woman.

716
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,310
When it comes to love,

717
00:34:03,440 --> 00:34:05,640
I always weigh the pros and cons,
playing it like a strategy.

718
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:08,070
Isn't that kind of awful?

719
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:10,480
Love is sometimes like a game.

720
00:34:11,570 --> 00:34:13,700
You need to find the balance
for the best outcome.

721
00:34:14,800 --> 00:34:16,360
Using a few tricks to protect yourself

722
00:34:16,630 --> 00:34:17,510
isn't wrong.

723
00:34:18,440 --> 00:34:19,280
Anything

724
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,550
is most appealing

725
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,440
when you start to doubt it

726
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,280
and want to break through it.

727
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,400
So our name is

728
00:34:26,670 --> 00:34:27,550
Boundary.

729
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,630
In this place,

730
00:34:28,630 --> 00:34:29,880
having such a big yard,

731
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:32,150
the owner must be someone special.

732
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:34,480
It's a private residence
of one of our members.

733
00:34:35,000 --> 00:34:37,360
They offered it
so we can hold exchanges here.

734
00:35:25,630 --> 00:35:27,670
Where are you?
The client's been waiting ages.

735
00:35:29,670 --> 00:35:30,550
I forgot.

736
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:31,800
Ah?

737
00:35:31,800 --> 00:35:32,640
You forgot?

738
00:35:34,670 --> 00:35:35,840
Weren't we supposed to sing?

739
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:37,960
Talk to him for a bit first.

740
00:35:38,710 --> 00:35:40,400
Me? What am I supposed to talk about?

741
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:41,510
The project's yours.

742
00:35:41,510 --> 00:35:42,880
The client specifically asked for you.

743
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:44,070
Would it look good
if you didn't show up?

744
00:35:46,320 --> 00:35:47,160
I'll be right there.

745
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:48,880
Need you, hurry over.

746
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:03,000
I'm going to meet the client.

747
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:04,230
You go to bed first.

748
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:05,190
Any women there?

749
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,000
Come along?

750
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:14,640
I'm not going.

751
00:36:15,710 --> 00:36:16,710
You go on your own.

752
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:18,760
And

753
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,920
if you think I did something with him,

754
00:36:24,230 --> 00:36:25,280
then go do it with someone else.

755
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:16,990
You're back.

756
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:18,230
Yeah.

757
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:19,510
I suddenly craved dumplings.

758
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:21,280
Thought I'd try making them myself.

759
00:37:21,990 --> 00:37:22,880
I made our

760
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:24,480
favorite cabbage and pork filling.

761
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,640
That's pretty great.

762
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:29,360
I remember my mom
taught me how to fold the edges.

763
00:37:29,360 --> 00:37:31,510
It seemed so easy then, so how come…

764
00:37:32,440 --> 00:37:35,280
So hard. This one looks so ugly.

765
00:37:36,920 --> 00:37:38,230
They look fine.

766
00:37:38,590 --> 00:37:39,480
Really?

767
00:37:39,480 --> 00:37:40,320
Super cute.

768
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:42,440
It looks terrible.

769
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:43,880
No, they're not.

770
00:37:45,320 --> 00:37:46,480
Then you eat more later.

771
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,600
Okay.

772
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,110
I haven't had homemade dumplings

773
00:38:05,110 --> 00:38:06,230
like this in ages.

774
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:08,960
Guess I need to
start learning to cook properly.

775
00:38:10,230 --> 00:38:11,070
Next time,

776
00:38:11,630 --> 00:38:12,670
I'll make it for you.

777
00:38:15,030 --> 00:38:15,870
Okay.

778
00:38:22,230 --> 00:38:23,110
Xiaoxi.

779
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:23,950
Mm?

780
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,800
Let's get married.

781
00:38:39,030 --> 00:38:40,150
I don't mean right now.

782
00:38:41,670 --> 00:38:43,000
I just wanted to tell you

783
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,840
my feelings for you have never changed.

784
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:50,030
I love this.

785
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,510
Dinner together after work every day.

786
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:54,760
Sharing life side by side.

787
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:57,550
I want this every single day.

788
00:38:59,760 --> 00:39:00,670
Is that okay?

789
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:06,130
♪There's no one
that I wouldn't try to fool♪

790
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:09,990
♪For an image of you♪

791
00:39:10,930 --> 00:39:13,040
♪Take my hand again♪

792
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:15,010
♪Take my mind again♪

793
00:39:15,100 --> 00:39:17,300
♪Break into my heart again♪

794
00:39:17,360 --> 00:39:19,320
If I can't guess
where this ball will land,

795
00:39:19,550 --> 00:39:22,360
even a black eight in
could make me lose the whole game.

796
00:39:22,900 --> 00:39:25,920
♪To beg for the truth♪

797
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:28,320
If one always
has the upper hand in a game,

798
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,760
wouldn't it get boring?

799
00:39:32,190 --> 00:39:33,480
Knowing there's a trap ahead,

800
00:39:34,440 --> 00:39:35,550
and walking in to take a look,

801
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:36,960
isn't that kind of fun?

802
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:40,890
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

803
00:39:40,900 --> 00:39:43,620
♪Did it come from above?♪

804
00:39:43,630 --> 00:39:44,960
Why do we need more drinks?

805
00:39:45,440 --> 00:39:47,550
Don't you think
we still don't really know each other?

806
00:39:48,440 --> 00:39:49,590
Have we gotten to know

807
00:39:49,590 --> 00:39:50,880
each other better these days?

808
00:39:52,590 --> 00:39:53,430
Not enough.

809
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,190
Let's play a truth game

810
00:39:57,190 --> 00:39:58,280
to speed things up.

811
00:39:58,280 --> 00:39:59,120
How?

812
00:39:59,710 --> 00:40:01,360
We take turns
asking each other a question.

813
00:40:02,230 --> 00:40:03,670
If the answer isn't satisfactory or

814
00:40:03,670 --> 00:40:04,510
you don't want to answer,

815
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:08,510
then drink a shot.

816
00:40:11,230 --> 00:40:12,070
Alright.

817
00:40:17,110 --> 00:40:17,950
You start first.

818
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:25,760
I'll go first.

819
00:40:28,710 --> 00:40:30,320
When we first started dating,

820
00:40:30,590 --> 00:40:32,440
girls hit on me

821
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,510
every now and then.

822
00:40:34,530 --> 00:40:35,760
Did you have anything to do with that?

823
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:39,510
Yeah.

824
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:42,440
I arranged it.

825
00:40:46,510 --> 00:40:47,510
Why'd you do that?

826
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,510
That's a different question.

827
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:55,960
Your ex-girlfriend's name is Zhen.

828
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,670
Zhen Guan and Zhen.

829
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:02,960
What's their relationship?

830
00:41:11,001 --> 00:41:13,600
♪I'll admit♪

831
00:41:13,601 --> 00:41:17,640
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

832
00:41:18,521 --> 00:41:22,387
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

833
00:41:22,412 --> 00:41:26,600
♪For this feeling to have you♪

834
00:41:26,881 --> 00:41:29,080
♪I'll resist♪

835
00:41:29,401 --> 00:41:31,415
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

836
00:41:31,440 --> 00:41:33,600
♪Your touches again♪

837
00:41:34,481 --> 00:41:38,461
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

838
00:41:38,486 --> 00:41:41,520
♪For an image of you♪

839
00:41:42,521 --> 00:41:44,960
♪Take my hand again♪

840
00:41:44,961 --> 00:41:46,720
♪Take my mind again♪

841
00:41:46,801 --> 00:41:50,160
♪Break into my heart again♪

842
00:41:50,561 --> 00:41:52,738
♪I'm falling out again♪

843
00:41:52,763 --> 00:41:54,600
♪I'm on my knees again♪

844
00:41:54,601 --> 00:41:58,440
♪To beg for the truth♪

845
00:42:00,281 --> 00:42:04,440
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

846
00:42:04,441 --> 00:42:09,440
♪Is that the secret to love♪

847
00:42:09,801 --> 00:42:12,760
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

848
00:42:12,841 --> 00:42:16,240
♪Did it come from above♪

849
00:42:16,321 --> 00:42:20,080
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

850
00:42:20,321 --> 00:42:25,400
♪Is that the secret to love♪

851
00:42:25,801 --> 00:42:28,240
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

